{"tid":818781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話啲快餐店做得慢","createTime":"2018-09-14T10:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T12:34:35.000Z","uid":208625,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"485945c25cbb7d4012fa47b139b2389a0c11f76d","tid":818781,"uid":208625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:36:56.000Z","msg":"啲人成日話快餐店啲員工做得慢，<br />\n但有無諗過係其他原因，<br />\n例如啲客好鐘意排到佢既時候，<br />\n先諗自己食咩餐，<br />\n問佢一樣先答一樣，<br />\n點解自己唔一次過講自己要啲咩？<br />\n比錢個陣又慢慢咁係自己個袋度攞錢出黎，<br />\n唔一早攞定。<br />\n當攞完喇，<br />\n準備找錢個陣，<br />\n先話自己有散銀，<br />\n依度都阻你幾分鐘做野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阻住地球轉"},{"pid":"856f615e4faf547ae3bc2cbd57d8ccf8314a79c6","tid":818781,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:43:51.000Z","msg":"有鳩人話你慢咩"},{"pid":"fac97a80be75454058ff04418206c79e2fc3224f","tid":818781,"uid":62983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"樓主做m記？"},{"pid":"4eefe9f2dccba6c4854fc8d7f482a03d726a5df3","tid":818781,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"KFC次次買餐都咁慢點解釋"},{"pid":"0c6c7a7d84fab857cdf26bc8fd4cc8f64de3fb38","tid":818781,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eefe9f2dccba6c4854fc8d7f482a03d726a5df3","tid":818781,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"KFC次次買餐都咁慢點解釋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:57:03.000Z","msg":"仲有人覺得佢係快餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657c5ab27c253a431d094bdedf3f1e79fdeb2043","tid":818781,"uid":10241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:00:06.000Z","msg":"一次過講自己要乜<br />\n然後下一秒又比人問番要乜<img s